  <Subject Subject_ID="300005253">
    <Parent_Relationships>
      <Preferred_Parent>
        <Parent_Subject_ID>300129541</Parent_Subject_ID>
        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>service industry buildings [300129541], commercial buildings [300005147], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings or parts of buildings designed or used for hairdressing, manicures, facials, and make-up application, typically having stalls or areas for individual hairdressers to do their work, large mirrors, and facilities for hairdryers and other equipment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046986/Webster's Third New International Dictionary (1986)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gebäude oder Gebäudeteile, die für das Frisieren, Maniküren, kosmetische Gesichtsbehandlungen und Make-up-Anwendungen bestimmt sind oder genutzt werden, typischerweise haben sie Stühle oder Bereiche für einzelne Friseure, damit diese ihre Arbeit verrichten können, große Spiegel und Anlagen für Haartrockner und weiteres Equipment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gebouwen of delen van gebouwen die zijn ontworpen of gebruikt voor kappers, manicures, gezichtsbehandelingen, en make-up aanbrenging, gewoonlijk met afgeschermde hokjes of ruimtes voor individuele kappers of specialisten om hun werk te doen. Meestal met grote spiegels, en faciliteiten voor haardrogers en andere apparatuur.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
